Titolo: Getsu F큰ma Den

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Getsu F큰ma Den is a side-scrolling action-adventure game for the Family Computer by Konami, released in 1987, and was available exclusively in Japan. It has been referenced in many subsequent Konami titles throughout the years. The game is structurally similar to Castlevania II: Simon's Quest, The Goonies II and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (NES). A hack-and-slash "roguevania" remake, titled Getsu F큰ma Den: Undying Moon, was released on Steam via Early Access on May 13, 2021 and will come out later for the Nintendo Switch in 2022. A sequel titled Shin Getsu F큰ma Den was planned for the PlayStation 2, but was cancelled.

